wei-gains?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>与澳大利亚设计、中国制造的视频会议机器人在工作场所挑战 Zoom、Google Meet</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/tech/tech-trends/article/3256523/meet-australian-designed-chinese-made-video-conferencing-robot-challenging-zoom-google-meet?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>Aubot 的 Teleport 由企业家 Marita Cheng 创建，是一款移动电话会议机器人，旨在提供更自然的社交体验。</description><pubDate>Sun, 24 Mar 2024 11:00:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/tech/tech-trends/article/3256523/meet-australian-designed-chinese-made-video-conferencing-robot-challenging-zoom-google-meet?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>“非常混乱”：莫斯科的中国学生分享音乐厅枪击事件的悲惨经历</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/diplomacy/article/3256517/it-was-very-chaotic-chinese-students-moscow-share-harrowing-accounts-concert-hall-shooting?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>来自中国北方的钢琴家躲在座位下躲过恐怖袭击，而另一名学生在俄罗斯首都发生枪击事件，造成 130 多人死亡，听到类似“鞭炮”的声音后逃离。</description><pubDate>Sun, 24 Mar 2024 09:00:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/diplomacy/article/3256517/it-was-very-chaotic-chinese-students-moscow-share-harrowing-accounts-concert-hall-shooting?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>意大利不再参与“一带一路”倡议，专注于与中国的战略关系，领导人今年受邀访问北京</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/article/3256511/no-longer-belt-and-road-initiative-italy-focuses-strategic-ties-china-leaders-invited-beijing-year?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>马西莫·安布罗塞蒂大使表示，在“积极的关系”中，意大利总统和总理计划今年进行访问。</description><pubDate>Sun, 24 Mar 2024 09:00:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/article/3256511/no-longer-belt-and-road-initiative-italy-focuses-strategic-ties-china-leaders-invited-beijing-year?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>中国最新的非洲建筑合同证明“体育场外交”是制胜法宝</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/diplomacy/article/3256360/chinas-latest-african-building-contracts-prove-stadium-diplomacy-winning-formula?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>